{"tid":1521837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"顏色水處理！唔好唔記得 鞋底同襪！","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:12:47.000Z","uid":181627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0dcad5d62fd7f935b0f42cfa2c99d08f60848c67","tid":1521837,"uid":181627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:06:11.000Z","msg":"洗唔甩嘅話就唔好要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n保障自己！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"b253134f27efa9890313e5942e1fc353a1933b98","tid":1521837,"uid":181627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"5f1316d5c945c785bfa09c60fff6559850e78829","tid":1521837,"uid":181627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"保護自己，加油手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8035eeec38ee70af602d872653a11f52a62b10d","tid":1521837,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"16e4382eec36518e38c467a5d9a4513965f78065","tid":1521837,"uid":181627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45375c8b3653d00d24ed92b7288838d75d660d24","tid":1521837,"uid":263708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"被染的手足應先離開現場"},{"pid":"3d6a99e428e96ef6c33b271b50601a5d29f22bad","tid":1521837,"uid":181627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ace322a7ef087611daa60ff7566f408123e6d40","tid":1521837,"uid":180663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}